# IDEAS For Project


## Basic Goals
1. Financial transactions storage/processing
    - track every money movement and log reliably
    - update balances and accounts reliably
2. Users and Financial accounts
    - Create, Read, Update, Delete Users
    - Track user balance (and transactions)
3. Authentication and Verification of Users
    - Authentication: only allowed persons can 
        access and transact through an account
    - Verification: only legal entities can 
        create and use an account
        (KYU - laws)
4. Multiple user options. eg:
    - MPesa
    - Visa
    - Airtel money


## Deeper Goals